## 3. MODULE BOUNDARIES

```
app/
├── ui/
│   ├── auth/           AuthScreen, AuthViewModel
│   ├── profile/        ProfileScreen, ProfileViewModel
│   ├── clubs/          ClubsListScreen, ClubDetailScreen, ClubViewModel
│   ├── games/          GamesListScreen, GameDetailScreen, GameViewModel
│   ├── bookings/       BookingsListScreen, BookingViewModel
│   ├── notifications/  NotificationsScreen, NotificationsViewModel
│   ├── chat/           ClubChatScreen, ClubChatViewModel
│   ├── reviews/        ReviewSheet, ReviewViewModel
│   ├── home/           HomeScreen, HomeViewModel
│   └── shared/         Reusable composables (cards, badges, avatars, etc.)
├── domain/
│   ├── model/          Domain models (separate from data models)
│   ├── usecase/        One class per use case (BookGameUseCase, CancelBookingUseCase, etc.)
│   └── mapper/         Data ↔ Domain model mappers
├── data/
│   ├── repository/     ClubRepository, GameRepository, BookingRepository,
│   │                   CreditRepository, ProfileRepository, NotificationRepository,
│   │                   ReviewRepository, ChatRepository
│   └── local/          DataStore access (DUPR cache, session state)
└── remote/
    ├── supabase/       SupabaseClient, all table queries and RPCs
    ├── stripe/         StripeService (PaymentSheet setup, PaymentIntent creation)
    └── fcm/            FcmTokenService (token registration, token refresh)
```

